<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:22:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国本周启动1万亿元刺激性债券发行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-kick-off-1-trillion-yuan-stimulus-bond-issues-this-week-2024-05-13/</link><description>中国财政部计划本周开始筹集期待已久的1万亿元人民币（1380亿美元）的长期特别国债，以筹集资金用于刺激疲软经济的关键领域。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 11:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-kick-off-1-trillion-yuan-stimulus-bond-issues-this-week-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：盈利障碍已扫清——CPI 接下来将上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-13/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟要求 Booking.com 必须遵守严格的技术规则，并对 X 进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-says-booking-must-comply-with-strict-tech-rules-investigates-x-2024-05-13/</link><description>欧盟委员会周一表示，已将酒店预订网站 Booking.com 指定为“看门人”，使其承担严格的欧盟义务，并已展开调查，以进一步确定社交媒体网络 X 的监管状况。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-says-booking-must-comply-with-strict-tech-rules-investigates-x-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>韩联社报道，中国呼吁在不受干扰的情况下加强与韩国的合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-top-diplomat-warns-rising-economic-competition-with-china-2024-05-13/</link><description>据首尔联合通讯社报道，中国外交部长王毅周一对韩国外长表示，中国和韩国面临着越来越多的困难，但应在不受干扰的情况下加强合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-top-diplomat-warns-rising-economic-competition-with-china-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中美在日内瓦会面讨论人工智能风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-china-meet-geneva-discuss-ai-risks-2024-05-13/</link><description>美国和中国将于周二在日内瓦会面讨论人工智能，美国官员强调，华盛顿的政策不会进行谈判，因为谈判将探讨如何减轻新兴技术带来的风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-china-meet-geneva-discuss-ai-risks-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国新关税对中国电动汽车和其他出口产品的打击有多大？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/how-hard-will-new-biden-tariffs-hit-china-2024-05-13/</link><description>据知情人士透露，美国总统乔·拜登将于周二宣布对中国征收新关税，目标包括电动汽车、医疗用品和太阳能设备等行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:57:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/how-hard-will-new-biden-tariffs-hit-china-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>德国称 2023 年外国行为者实施的网络犯罪增加了 28%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-says-cybercrime-by-foreign-actors-rose-by-28-2023-2024-05-13/</link><description>周一发布的数据显示，2023 年德国外国犯罪者的网络犯罪激增，比上一年增长了 28%，而欧洲在选举前夕对涉嫌俄罗斯黑客和间谍的担忧加剧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:49:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-says-cybercrime-by-foreign-actors-rose-by-28-2023-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>三名男子在英国法庭出庭，被控帮助香港外国情报部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-charge-three-men-with-helping-hong-kongs-foreign-intelligence-service-2024-05-13/</link><description>三名被控协助香港驻英国外国情报部门的男子周一在伦敦一家法院出庭，此前他们在英国各地遭到一系列逮捕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 07:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-charge-three-men-with-helping-hong-kongs-foreign-intelligence-service-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>日本软银转向季度盈利，关注 Arm 部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/softbank-swings-q4-profit-21-bln-2024-05-13/</link><description>日本软银集团周一表示，尽管其愿景基金部门的投资损失凸显了该技术投资者面临的挑战，包括实现其宏伟的人工智能雄心，但该公司在本财年最后一个季度扭亏为盈。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 06:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/softbank-swings-q4-profit-21-bln-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司的亏损表明其难以填补欧盟与中国的天然气销售缺口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gazprom-loss-shows-struggle-fill-eu-gas-sales-gap-with-china-2024-05-13/</link><description>克里姆林宫旗下的能源巨头俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司（Gazprom）曾经是俄罗斯最赚钱的公司，但由于其国内市场和中国出口难以填补欧洲天然气销售损失的缺口，该公司可能会面临长期业绩不佳的局面。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 06:04:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gazprom-loss-shows-struggle-fill-eu-gas-sales-gap-with-china-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>WPIC 表示，供应疲软将导致 2024 年铂金缺口高于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weaker-supply-will-drive-platinum-deficit-higher-than-expected-2024-wpic-says-2024-05-13/</link><description>世界铂金投资理事会 (WPIC) 周一表示，由于南非和俄罗斯矿山供应减少，2024 年全球铂金短缺将比此前预期更深。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 05:10:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weaker-supply-will-drive-platinum-deficit-higher-than-expected-2024-wpic-says-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：随着美国通货膨胀，每一位小数都很重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-05-13/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 05:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行承诺支持经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国央行周五表示，将确保流动性合理充裕和信贷扩张，巩固经济复苏，但经济复苏仍面临诸多挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：Shein 在美国上市遇到障碍的情况下加紧伦敦 IPO 准备工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</link><description>消息人士称，如果此次IPO成功，可能会成为今年全球规模最大的IPO之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商 Zeekr 在美国上市表现出色，股价飙升近 35%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五，Zeekr 的股价较首次公开募股价格上涨近 35%，这为这家电动汽车制造商带来了强劲的开局，这是自 2021 年以来首家中国公司在美国主要市场首次亮相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>